Cristiano Ronaldo is widely regarded as one of the greatest footballers of all time. Born on February 5, 1985, in Madeira, Portugal, he rose from humble beginnings to become a global sports icon. Known for his incredible speed, powerful shots, and unmatched work ethic, Ronaldo has played for top clubs like Manchester United, Real Madrid, Juventus, and Al-Nassr. He has won numerous titles, including multiple Ballon d'Or awards and Champions League trophies. Off the pitch, Ronaldo is admired for his discipline, philanthropy, and massive influence on social media, making him not just a football legend but also a global ambassador for the sport. He is the undisputed goat